        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Existence may be borne, and the deep root Of life and sufferance make its firm abode In bare and desolate bosoms: mute The camel labours with the heaviest load, And the wolf dies in silence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281511_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281511/8172_281511_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Filled with the face of heaven, which, from afar, Comes down upon the waters; all its hues, From the rich sunset to the rising star, Their magical variety diffuse: And now they change; a paler shadow strews Its mantle o'er the mountains; parting day Dies like the dolphin, whom each pang imbues With a new colour as it gasps away, The last still loveliest, till-'tis gone-and all is grey.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281511_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281511/8172_281511_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "He arose To raise a language, and his land reclaim From the dull yoke of her barbaric foes: Watering the tree which bears his lady's name With his melodious tears, he gave himself to fame.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281511_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281511/8172_281511_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "And Tasso is their glory and their shame. Hark to his strain! and then survey his cell! And see how dearly earned Torquato's fame, And where Alfonso bade his poet dwell. The miserable despot could not quell The insulted mind he sought to quench, and blend With the surrounding maniacs, in the hell Where he had plunged it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281511_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281511/8172_281511_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Peace to Torquato's injured shade!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "The Niobe of nations!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Alas, the lofty city! and alas The trebly hundred triumphs! and the day When Brutus made the dagger's edge surpass The conqueror's sword in bearing fame away! Alas for Tully's voice, and Virgil's lay, And Livy's pictured page!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "But these shall be Her resurrection; all beside-decay. Alas for Earth, for never shall we see That brightness in her eye she bore when Rome was free!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "See What crimes it costs to be a moment free And famous through all ages!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "The fool of false dominion-and a kind Of bastard Caesar, following him of old With steps unequal; for the Roman's mind Was modelled in a less terrestrial mould, With passions fiercer, yet a judgment cold, And an immortal instinct which redeemed The frailties of a heart so soft, yet bold. Alcides with the distaff now he seemed At Cleopatra's feet, and now himself he beamed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "And came, and saw, and conquered.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "But the man Who would have tamed his eagles down to flee, Like a trained falcon, in the Gallic van, Which he, in sooth, long led to victory, With a deaf heart which never seemed to be A listener to itself, was strangely framed; With but one weakest weakness-vanity: Coquettish in ambition, still he aimed At what?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281514_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281514/8172_281514_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Can he avouch, or answer what he claimed?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281515_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281515/8172_281515_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Can tyrants but by tyrants conquered be, And Freedom find no champion and no child Such as Columbia saw arise when she Sprung forth a Pallas, armed and undefiled? Or must such minds be nourished in the wild, Deep in the unpruned forest, midst the roar Of cataracts, where nursing nature smiled On infant Washington?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281515_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281515/8172_281515_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "But who was she, the lady of the dead, Tombed in a palace?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281515_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281515/8172_281515_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Was she chaste and fair? Worthy a king's-or more-a Roman's bed? What race of chiefs and heroes did she bear? What daughter of her beauties was the heir? How lived-how loved-how died she?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281515_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281515/8172_281515_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Was she as those who love their lords, or they Who love the lords of others?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281515_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281515/8172_281515_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "such have been Even in the olden time, Rome's annals say. Was she a matron of Cornelia's mien, Or the light air of Egypt's graceful queen, Profuse of joy; or 'gainst it did she war, Inveterate in virtue?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281515_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281515/8172_281515_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Did she lean To the soft side of the heart, or wisely bar Love from amongst her griefs?--for such the affections are.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8172_281515_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8172/281515/8172_281515_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Where is the rock of Triumph, the high place Where Rome embraced her heroes?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
