        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8172",
        "content": "Yes; and in yon field below, A thousand years of silenced factions sleep- The Forum, where the immortal accents glow, And still the eloquent air breathes-burns with Cicero!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
